ua không gian âm nhạc sôi động mà chiếc&nbsp;<a href=\"https://fptshop.com.vn/phu-kien/tai-nghe\" title=\"Tai nghe chính hãng\" type=\"Tai nghe chính hãng\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; color: rgb(1, 104, 250); vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">tai nghe</a>&nbsp;đem lại.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 11px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); line-height: 24px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"Chống nước tai nghe AirPods 3\" id=\"\" src=\"https://fptshop.com.vn/Uploads/images/2015/Tin-Tuc/BaoPK/HDCameraZenfoneLaser/mo-ta-san-pham-airpods-3-4.JPG\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; background: transparent; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 6px; width: 665px; height: auto !important;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 11px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Hòa mình vào âm thanh vòm sống động<